      "semantic_score": 0.249,
      "formant_ratio": 0.735,
      "token_count": 56,
      "speaker_turn": false,
      "text": " Because of this, it's critical that you understand your market, which is to say your customer and their problems, competitors, primary, secondary, and tertiary, product, and its place in the broader market, and your market, current share, and growth opportunities."
    },
